            "id": "https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus",
            "content_html": "<p>Let‚Äôs compare the most popular modern Java frameworks.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"startup-time-comparison\">Startup Time Comparison<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#startup-time-comparison\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Startup Time Comparison\" title=\"Direct link to Startup Time Comparison\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h2>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>Framework</th><th>Startup Time</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Spring Boot</td><td>1500‚Äì2500ms</td></tr><tr><td>Micronaut</td><td>600‚Äì1200ms</td></tr><tr><td>Quarkus</td><td>800‚Äì1500ms</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Korus</strong></td><td><strong>120‚Äì250ms</strong></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"dependency-injection-model\">Dependency Injection Model<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#dependency-injection-model\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Dependency Injection Model\" title=\"Direct link to Dependency Injection Model\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h2>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>Framework</th><th>DI Style</th><th>Reflection?</th><th>Compile-Time?</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Spring Boot</td><td>Runtime DI</td><td>Yes</td><td>Partial</td></tr><tr><td>Micronaut</td><td>Compile-Time DI</td><td>No</td><td>Yes</td></tr><tr><td>Quarkus</td><td>Build-Time DI</td><td>Some</td><td>Mostly</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Korus</strong></td><td><strong>Build-Time DI</strong></td><td><strong>Some</strong></td><td><strong>Mostly</strong></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"architecture-differences\">Architecture Differences<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#architecture-differences\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Architecture Differences\" title=\"Direct link to Architecture Differences\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h2>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"spring-boot\">Spring Boot<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#spring-boot\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Spring Boot\" title=\"Direct link to Spring Boot\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"\">Heavy runtime logic</li>\n<li class=\"\">Massive ecosystem</li>\n<li class=\"\">Easiest to use</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"micronaut\">Micronaut<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#micronaut\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Micronaut\" title=\"Direct link to Micronaut\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"\">Build-time friendly</li>\n<li class=\"\">Faster than Spring</li>\n<li class=\"\">Requires extra modules</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"quarkus\">Quarkus<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#quarkus\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Quarkus\" title=\"Direct link to Quarkus\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"\">GraalVM optimized</li>\n<li class=\"\">Build-time profiling</li>\n<li class=\"\">Complex stack</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"korus\">Korus<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#korus\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Korus\" title=\"Direct link to Korus\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"\"><strong>Simpler than Micronaut/Quarkus</strong></li>\n<li class=\"\"><strong>Faster than all of them</strong></li>\n<li class=\"\"><strong>Pure compile-time graph</strong></li>\n<li class=\"\"><strong>Clean Undertow runtime</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"when-to-choose-which\">When to choose which?<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#when-to-choose-which\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to When to choose which?\" title=\"Direct link to When to choose which?\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h2>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>Use Case</th><th>Best Choice</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Enterprise backend</td><td>Spring Boot</td></tr><tr><td>Serverless</td><td>Korus / Quarkus</td></tr><tr><td>Microservices</td><td>Korus / Micronaut</td></tr><tr><td>CLI apps</td><td>Korus</td></tr><tr><td>AOT native images</td><td>Korus / Quarkus</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorTargetHideOnScrollNavbar_vjPI\" id=\"final-verdict\">Final Verdict<a href=\"https://korus-projects.github.io/blog/korus-vs-spring-micronaut-quarkus#final-verdict\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Final Verdict\" title=\"Direct link to Final Verdict\" translate=\"no\">‚Äã</a></h2>\n<p>Korus is ideal when you want:</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"\">Fast startup</li>\n<li class=\"\">Low memory usage</li>\n<li class=\"\">Deterministic DI</li>\n<li class=\"\">Zero reflection runtime</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Korus stands as a <strong>next-generation framework</strong> built for modern Java workloads.</p>",
